&lt;p&gt;At Samsung Research America, we believe interns are pivotal to our community and success. We offer a variety of internship opportunities across our R&amp;amp;D labs for both undergraduates and postgraduates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you’re interested in joining Samsung Research America&#39;s Internship Program but don&#39;t see an opportunity that you&#39;d like to apply to, please share your resume here. We&#39;ll keep your information on file and will reach out if we find a match!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Learn more about our Internship Program on our SRA site: &lt;a href=&quot;https://sra.samsung.com/internships/&quot;&gt;Internships - Samsung Research America&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional Information &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
